divs: sighting detailsi took this picture while on a factory tour of the appleton estate, i jamaica. ( april 8th 2009) i didn't noticed anything back then. i just saw this as i was reviewing the pictures. i have another picture taken within a minute of this one and there's nothing in the sky. you can see it was a beautiful sunny day, low winds, little\no clouds. i know this could be anything... but i'd like to contact other people from that tour that might have taken some pictures like mine.
